---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About Us" 
  description="Learn about Arcdome, our privacy-first client-side image optimization tools, and how we deliver speed and security."
>
  <div class="about-page">
    <div class="header-section">
      <h1 class="page-title">About Arcdome</h1>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Pioneering secure, serverless browser-based image utility tools.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Core Intro Card -->
    <div class="glass-card intro-card">
      <div class="intro-text">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          At <strong>Arcdome</strong>, we believe image optimization should be fast, free, and secure. Most image tools online force you to upload your files to external servers. This process is not only slow and bandwidth-intensive, but it also creates severe privacy and security risks for sensitive documents, personal photos, and corporate assets.
        </p>
        <p>
          We set out to build a platform that completely solves these problems. By leveraging modern HTML5 Canvas, Blob, and Javascript APIs, our tools process your images <strong>entirely inside your web browser</strong>. Your files never touch a cloud server. They are compressed, converted, and resized instantly on your local device.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="logo-display">
        <svg class="about-logo" width="80" height="80" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <defs>
            <linearGradient id="aboutLogoGrad" x1="0" y1="0" x2="36" y2="36" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
              <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#00f2fe" />
              <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#4facfe" />
            </linearGradient>
          </defs>
          <rect x="4" y="4" width="20" height="20" rx="6" stroke="url(#aboutLogoGrad)" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linejoin="round" />
          <rect x="12" y="12" width="20" height="20" rx="6" fill="url(#aboutLogoGrad)" fill-opacity="0.15" stroke="url(#aboutLogoGrad)" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linejoin="round" />
          <circle cx="14" cy="14" r="2.5" fill="#00f2fe" />
          <path d="M7 21L12.5 15.5L20 23" stroke="#00f2fe" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" />
          <path d="M15 28.5L20.5 23L27.5 30" stroke="#00f2fe" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" />
        </svg>
        <h3>Arcdome</h3>
        <span>Version 1.0 (Stable)</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature Grid -->
    <div class="features-section">
      <h2 class="sub-title">Why Arcdome Stands Out</h2>
      <div class="features-grid">
        
        <div class="glass-card feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2" />
              <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>100% Privacy-First</h3>
          <p>Since all operations run locally in your client memory, we do not store, view, or parse any of your visual content. Your files stay yours.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Instant Processing</h3>
          <p>No more queue systems or upload delays. High-performance canvas-rendering resizes and converts your images in milliseconds.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M12 2v20M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Completely Free</h3>
          <p>No subscription, no watermark, and no premium gates. Access our full suite of compressor, converter, and resizer tools unlimitedly.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M4.5 16.5c-1.5 1.26-2.5 3.19-2.5 5.5h20c0-2.31-1-4.24-2.5-5.5" />
              <path d="M12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12c0 2.3.8 4.4 2.1 6.1" />
              <path d="M12 22c5.5 0 10-4.5 10-10 0-2.3-.8-4.4-2.1-6.1" />
              <path d="M12 6a6 6 0 0 0-6 6c0 .8.2 1.5.5 2.1" />
              <path d="M18 12a6 6 0 0 0-5.5-5.9" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>SEO & Speed Core</h3>
          <p>Built with Astro 7, compiling to server-side static html with zero hydration locks, guaranteeing 100/100 page speed metrics.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Tech Stack Section -->
    <div class="tech-section">
      <div class="glass-card tech-card">
        <h2>Technology & Operations</h2>
        <p>
          Arcdome utilizes Astro for layout structures and page compilation. 
          The core processing engine is built using standard native browser modules, including `CanvasRenderingContext2D` for high-quality image rescaling, `HTMLCanvasElement.toBlob()` for compression adjustments, and async file readers. This means we keep the JavaScript bundles extremely small, leading to faster initial loads and better SEO indexing scores.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .header-section {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    background: var(--gradient-text);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .intro-card {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
    gap: 40px;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .intro-card {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      padding: 32px;
      gap: 32px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .logo-display {
      order: -1;
    }
  }

  .intro-text h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: var(--text-main);
  }

  .intro-text p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  /* Logo Display Card Box */
  .logo-display {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 32px;
  }

  .about-logo {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .logo-display h3 {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .logo-display span {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }



  /* Features */
  .features-section {
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .sub-title {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: var(--text-main);
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .feature-card {
    padding: 32px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: #f1f5f9;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    color: #475569;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* Tech Card styling */
  .tech-section {
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .tech-card {
    padding: 32px 40px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    background: #ffffff;
  }

  .tech-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
</style>
